oint </b>are published in the two languages.</p>"}{"richtext":"<h2>Section Policies</h2>\n<h3><b>Close-up</b></h3>\n<p>The main section of each issue contains peer-reviewed academic articles (in two language versions) devoted to the theme of a given issue. Upcoming themes are announced in the <a href=\"http://pismowidok.org/index.php/one/announcement\">CFP</a> tab.</p>\n<h3><b>Panorama</b></h3>\n<p>The section contains peer-reviewed academic articles not necessarily related to the leading theme of the issue. Please feel invited to submit articles relevant to the journal profile regardless of the dates of publication of the next thematic issues.</p>\n<h3><b>Perspectives</b></h3>\n<p>This section embraces discussions held by the editorial team and with invited guests, interviews and conversations, curatorial texts and commentaries on the leading theme of the issue.</p>\n<h3><b>Viewpoint</b></h3>\n<p>The section features artistic projects and other presentations of visual materials of interest in the context of the leading theme of the issue.</p>\n<h3><b>Snapshots</b></h3>\n<p>This section presents reviews of publications, exhibitions, theatre plays, films, etc.</p>\n<p> </p>"}";s:8:"richtext";s:1:"1";s:8:"template";s:1:"4";s:9:"menuindex";s:1:"0";s:10:"searchable";s:1:"1";s:9:"cacheable";s:1:"1";s:9:"createdby";s:1:"1";s:9:"createdon";s:10:"1527241571";s:8:"editedby";s:2:"17";s:8:"editedon";s:10:"1567113246";s:7:"deleted";s:1:"0";s:9:"deletedon";s:1:"0";s:9:"deletedby";s:1:"0";s:11:"publishedon";s:10:"1527241615";s:11:"publishedby";s:1:"1";s:9:"menutitle";s:0:"";s:7:"donthit";s:1:"0";s:11:"haskeywords";s:1:"0";s:11:"hasmetatags";s:1:"0";s:10:"privateweb";s:1:"0";s:10:"privatemgr";s:1:"0";s:13:"content_dispo";s:1:"0";s:8:"hidemenu";s:1:"0";s:13:"alias_visible";s:1:"1";s:14:"sitemapInclude";a:5:{i:0;s:14:"sitemapInclude";i:1;s:1:"1";i:2;s:0:"";i:3;s:0:"";i:4;s:16:"custom_tv:switch";}s:15:"sitemapPriority";a:5:{i:0;s:15:"sitemapPriority";i:1;s:3:"0.5";i:2;s:0:"";i:3;s:0: